/09/the-playlist-new-bands-with-the-prettiots-dua-lipa-and-mind-enterprises |title=The playlist: new bands \u2013 with the Prettiots, Dua Lipa and Mind Enterprises |work=The Guardian |date=9 November 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Last Dance\"\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 2016\n| Jon Brewer and Ian Blair\n| <ref>{{cite web|last=Hunt|first=El|url=http://diymag.com/2016/02/18/dua-lipa-shares-video-for-last-dance|title=Dua Lipa shares video for 'Last Dance'|work=[[DIY (magazine)|DIY]]|date=18 February 2016|accessdate=7 November 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Hotter than Hell\"\n| [[Emil Nava]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|last=Spanos|first=Brittany|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/watch-dua-lipas-steamy-hotter-than-hell-video-20160506|title=Watch Dua Lipa's Steamy 'Hotter Than Hell' Video|work=[[Rolling Stone]]|date=6 May 2016|accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Blow Your Mind (Mwah)\"\n| [[Kinga Burza]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|last=Renshaw|first=David|url=http://www.thefader.com/2016/09/12/dua-lipa-blow-your-mind-mwah-video|title=Dua Lipa Shares \"Blow Your Mind (Mwah)\" Video|work=The Fader|date=12 September 2016|accessdate=12 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Room for 2\"\n| Vicky Lawton\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hungertv.com/feature/premiere-dua-lipas-video-for-room-for-2/|title=PREMIERE: Dua Lipa's video for Room For 2|publisher=Hunger TV|date=3 November 2016|accessdate=7 November 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Be the One\" {{small|(second version)}}\n| [[Daniel Kaufman (director)|Daniel Kaufman]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://imvdb.com/video/dua-lipa/be-the-one/2|title=Dua Lipa \u2013 Be The One (Version 2) (2016)|publisher=IMVDb|accessdate=23 December 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Scared to Be Lonely\"<br>{{small|(with Martin Garrix)}}\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2017\n| Blake Claridge\n| <ref name=\"Scared\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/7669858/martin-garrix-dua-lipa-scared-to-be-lonely|tit